Sentencas: Scanning electron microscopy and cyclic voltammetry were used to investigate the high-temperature oxidation behavior of two solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels

Sentencas: One alloy had a low content of manganese; the other alloy had a high content of manganese.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels

Sentencas: Four reduction and four oxidation peaks were observed in the voltammograms of the low manganese alloy at a temperature of 800 A degrees C.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels

Sentencas: The voltammograms of the alloy with a high content of manganese were different.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels

Sentencas: At 600 A degrees C, three reduction peaks and two oxidation peaks were observed.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels

Sentencas: At 800 A degrees C, additional peaks were observed in the voltammogram for this alloy.
Titulo: A combined SEM and CV study of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect steels
